law.text:
As used in this chapter:
"Department" means the Department of Kentucky State Police;
"Commissioner" means the commissioner of the Department of Kentucky State Police;
"Driver training" means instruction of persons in the operation of motor vehicles which are not commercial motor vehicles;
"Driver training school" means any person, firm, partnership, association or corporation which offers a course of driver training for which a fee or tuition is charged; and
"Person," when referring to a driver training school, means person, firm, partnership, association, or corporation.
